§ 214. Previous laws unaffected Nothing in this chapter shall be construed as modifying or revoking any of the provisions of sections 191 to 193 11 See References in Text note below. of this title. (Mar. 3, 1915, ch. 74, § 13, 38 Stat. 822.)
